10 An Act relating to volunteer firefighters;
establishing the Oklahoma Volunteer Firefighter
11 Support Program; creating a grant program; allowing
for a certain number of training hours; providing for
12 certification of training; requiring an application
process; allowing for promulgation of rules; creating
13 the Oklahoma Volunteer Firefighter Support Revolving
Fund; providing for codification; and providing an
14 effective date.
15
